snippet.title: Craft Keep VR - Early Access Trailer [VR, HTC Vive]
snippet.description:
Early Access trailer for Craft Keep VR, a virtual reality game that lets you become a blacksmith in a fantasy world. Developed by Arvydas Žemaitis, available for HTC Vive. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/craft-keep-vr
